# Weather App (CLI)

A command-line app to fetch weather data for a city using a weather API.

## Features

- Fetch current weather by city name
- Shows temperature, humidity, conditions

## Technologies

- Python
- requests module
- OpenWeatherMap API (or similar)

## How to Run

```bash
python weather.py
